# DisplayProjekt — Development Logbook

A structured repository tracking the exploration and implementation of physical, mechanical, and alternative display systems.

---

## 📅 May 2026

### 🛠️ May 27, 2026 — Orbital Indicator Concept
*   **Concept Exploration:** Investigated using an orbital, clock-like mechanical movement to visualize metrics (e.g., tracking the quantity or status of coffee orders). The rotary layout offers an elegant, non-digital approach to data physicalization.
*   **Design Reference:** 
    *   [Desk Orbital Clock Version 2.0 (MakerWorld)](https://makerworld.com/en/models/788000-desk-orbital-clock-version-2-0) — *Inspiration for the mechanical drive and ring-based positioning.*
*   **Artifacts:** Generated a conceptual rendering/image illustrating how this orbital metric display could look and function within the physical housing.

---

### 🔬 May 23, 2026 — Mechanical & Electro-Magnetic Displays
*   **Flip-Dot Display Evaluation:**
    *   Evaluated a vintage/traditional Flip-Dot display unit.
    *   *Finding:* Integrating and driving the legacy hardware with a Raspberry Pi appears highly complex and requires significant custom circuitry/driver overhead.
    *   *Technical References:*
        *   [How-to: Flip-dot With a Raspberry Pi (Instructables)](https://www.instructables.com/Howto-Flipdot-With-a-Raspi/)
        *   [Der Flipdot-Hack (Heise Ratgeber)](https://www.heise.de/ratgeber/Der-Flipdot-Hack-3527908.html)
*   **Split-Flap Display Research:**
    *   Explored modular, 3D-printable split-flap mechanisms as a more maintainable and customizable mechanical alternative to commercial flip-dots.
    *   *Technical Reference:* [Split-Flap Clock Digit Unit (MakerWorld)](https://makerworld.com/en/models/1032884-split-flap-clock-digit-unit?from=search#profileId-1016086)
*   **Potential Offshoots / Side Concepts:**
    *   Considered a personalized or decorative split-flap application (e.g., for Jessica).
    *   *Reference:* [Split-Flap Picture Frame (MakerWorld)](https://makerworld.com/en/models/1096415-split-flap-picture-frame)

