## 📋 How to use this Logbook
1. **Add Entries:** Always add new entries at the top of the log under the corresponding month header (reverse chronological order).
2. **Link Assets:** Store physical sketches, conceptual renders, or wiring diagrams in an `/assets` or `/images` directory within the repository and link them directly using `![Alt Text](assets/filename.png)`.
3. **Cross-Reference:** Link components to active code or hardware BOM lists where relevant.
